Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.34,0:00:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.30,0:00:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.26,0:00:19.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天在後山好像發生了戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.50,0:00:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.55,0:00:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀 好像出現了別國的間諜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警衛部隊打倒了其中一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.63,0:00:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且回收了屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.12,0:00:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來今天別讓學生們靠近後山比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許還留有殘黨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.10,0:00:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願平安無事才好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,屍體呢 屍體呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底在哪兒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然經常在這附近晃悠比較熟悉 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.63,0:01:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該問一下他們詳細的地點來著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.27,0:01:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹嗎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.48,0:01:07.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上回學校去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.65,0:01:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.11,0:01:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡依舊有危險分子存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.58,0:01:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受人所托 怎麼能半途而廢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.88,0:01:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.53,0:01:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是你的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.45,0:01:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.89,0:01:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為啥只有這種時候才擺出一副老師的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.27,0:01:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師根本不理解我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.31,0:01:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我回學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.66,0:01:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不會改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我總是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.97,0:01:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是被同伴疏遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不關心我的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這次不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我將戰利品帶回去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.65,0:01:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就會認同我這個夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.35,0:01:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我就不再是孤單一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不想體會那種感受了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.21,0:02:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我一定要將戰利品帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管你有什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.72,0:02:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.15,0:02:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕不能讓你留在這座危險的後山裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.93,0:02:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我的心情…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必殺 色誘術
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:37.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.79,0:02:39.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人還真是單純
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.62,0:02:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…戰鬥過的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.67,0:02:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 在這附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.87,0:03:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真頭痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我今天什麼都沒吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.49,0:03:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼可吃的東西呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.57,0:03:17.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到午餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.83,0:03:20.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種形狀我從沒見過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.83,0:03:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一定是昨天戰鬥時 敵方忍者用的苦無了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來 我找到戰利品了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把苦無
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是我們要尋找的密函嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.29,0:03:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來在被打倒之前 他把苦無藏在了鳥窩裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:59.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪兒去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是個麻煩的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.42,0:04:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便應付一下他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子…就這樣吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.52,0:04:15.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人說的沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.56,0:04:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他一點也不瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.34,0:04:22.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母雙亡後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也沒有人誇獎我 認可我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在班上 我經常幹蠢事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我希望被人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟當時的我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以借我點錢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.16,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 你把零花錢全花在零食上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了零食 我還能花在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.89,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿你沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借你一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還在上課吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.96,0:07:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能跟陌生人說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.78,0:07:19.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則老爸會跟我發火的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.65,0:07:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈良鹿丸和秋道丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.21,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會知道我們的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.77,0:07:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是鹿角和丁座的兒子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長得真像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:34.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你們翹課的事告訴他們好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.99,0:07:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天改自習課了 是吧 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人去後山找屍體了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師隨後就去找他了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師去找鳴人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此話當真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 千真萬確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 自習不代表下課了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.93,0:08:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快回學校去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.16,0:08:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.15,0:08:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣我也有同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 你們是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖將那把苦無交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 這個我絕對不會給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 看來我們得動粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.36,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.03,0:08:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色誘術
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾 這個術可不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:08:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.86,0:09:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直就是犯規啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.49,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此 分身術
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.91,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是個小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次見到這麼不中用的分身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.35,0:09:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.03,0:09:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍術如果不管用的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓他跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.97,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對這座森林裡佈置的陷阱可是瞭如指掌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.47,0:09:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 怎麼能被這種不入流的陷阱…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.67,0:09:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小兔崽子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有一個陷阱在哪兒來著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:09:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.21,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.06,0:10:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清醒點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受傷了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事了 一起回學校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.79,0:10:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.16,0:10:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些外人在木葉鬼鬼祟祟地想幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.00,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老實實地把那個小鬼交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.55,0:10:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.50,0:10:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照顧這個傻瓜學生很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.18,0:10:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此你也要小命不保了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越傻越可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且我也不是那麼容易被幹掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.08,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 振作一點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.17,0:11:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 包圍他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會保護好鳴人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想跑 散
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影多重手裡劍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲不掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.91,0:12:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你的學生那聽到了一些消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些放心不下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.11,0:12:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增援來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.29,0:12:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起收拾而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火遁連攜術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走 伊魯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.93,0:12:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迦樓羅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉一個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.51,0:12:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.27,0:12:44.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是卡卡西先生及時趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅憑我一人 怕是難以脫險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.38,0:12:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有你一個 也能保護好鳴人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.82,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我似乎有些明白卡卡西先生的那番話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.09,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未直面過鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.57,0:13:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是在不斷地迴避著他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今後我一定會直面鳴人的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…木葉村的警衛部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是她們潛入的目的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.61,0:13:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.63,0:13:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡快調整村裡的警備部署
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.99,0:13:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說事出偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次鳴人的莽撞反而拯救了村子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.45,0:13:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以退下了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.90,0:13:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三代
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.25,0:13:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您讓我成為了鳴人的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.79,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因此我才會想起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.69,0:14:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾經我決定做一名老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.48,0:14:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為您那時對我的一番教誨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經一年過去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.34,0:14:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將悲傷壓抑在笑容之下 很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.48,0:14:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你班主任那兒聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在學校裡總是大家開心的焦點
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.06,0:14:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…才沒有悲傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者死於任務是一種榮譽
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.04,0:14:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親也好 母親也好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是用性命從妖狐手中保衛了村子的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我則是英雄之子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.59,0:15:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不會孤單 不會難過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是喜悅之淚…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你總是孤單一人抱膝而坐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:14.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你並非孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.71,0:15:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉村的忍者們都擁有火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.52,0:15:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想要保衛這個村子的強烈願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是擁有這個意志的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村裡的大伙們都是他的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.55,0:15:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡 你有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.85,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想將第三代的火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.73,0:15:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳給後人 傳給鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 為啥將我辛苦找回的戰利品給弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.20,0:16:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.79,0:16:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那個 你差點丟了小命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那倒也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.34,0:16:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎麼這麼聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.27,0:16:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓我第一次看到伊魯卡老師發這麼大火呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你嚇到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師決定以後要好好關注你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 從明天起會嚴格調教你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愈發不想去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 你擁有火之意志嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.01,0:16:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火之意志 那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.01,0:16:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂火之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.43,0:16:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是想要保護這個村子的強烈願望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你擁有它的話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:16:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能變得如火影大人般的強大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影真的那麼厲害嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.65,0:17:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 不只是厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.07,0:17:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影大人還深受村民們的敬仰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.29,0:17:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引領我們的領袖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.47,0:17:13.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是第四代
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可是從妖狐手中保護了村子的英雄哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.86,0:17:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要成為比第四代更厲害的火影
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後用我的力量得到大家的認同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.39,0:17:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等你長這麼高的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許就能當上火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.52,0:17:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會拚命努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.03,0:17:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成功給你看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.43,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒準真能成為火影哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊魯卡老師 過來幫幫忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我這就過來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.32,0:18:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.44,0:18:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩三天前出去後就沒回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.83,0:18:35.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好別回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.08,0:18:37.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都聽到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬首大刀…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還惦記著它啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就怪你當時沒帶上它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.02,0:18:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我找得好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.66,0:18:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和八尾那種怪物交戰時
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰還有空管這種累贅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.25,0:18:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把半死不活的你們扛回來的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:57.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別內訌了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真以恩人自居了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.98,0:19:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管他呢 反正也找回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少了它果然缺乏鬥志啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下人都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體準備出發
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷勢痊癒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.77,0:19:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面前往木葉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.60,0:19:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到佩因會戰敗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是大跌眼鏡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小南也不會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 一下子少了這麼多人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還需要一個能和外道魔像同步的棋子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼鮫 你去找八尾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:56.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有其他事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.16,0:20:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會這麼慘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.06,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說鳴人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這是佩因所為
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.23,0:20:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過鳴人已經解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.82,0:20:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打倒了佩因
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人他…那九尾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他憑借自己的力量壓制了九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.93,0:20:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人自己將九尾…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可沒工夫讓你吃驚了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來重建村子可不輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.39,0:20:48.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大和 我們需要你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.19,0:20:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.30,0:20:55.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召開緊急會議了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上忍班長鹿角先生 請立刻前往大名殿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.60,0:22:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是鳴人的家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.61,0:22:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是個傻小子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由你來負責教導最為合適
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.61,0:22:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外宇智波佐助也在你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.74,0:23:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不會那麼簡單就心慈手軟的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.61,0:23:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:04.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你順利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指導上忍 旗木卡卡西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.98,0:23:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來相當棘手啊
